18:56.446 --> 18:58.044
Thank you for forgiving me.

18:58.046 --> 18:59.444
It's okay.

18:59.446 --> 19:02.316
At some point, we were bound
to have our first fight.

19:02.318 --> 19:04.316
Well, it almost happened
when you called

19:04.318 --> 19:06.556
my apple pie crust “doughy”"

19:08.358 --> 19:10.354
The truth is
you were right.

19:10.356 --> 19:13.161
And I was just
angry at myself.

19:13.163 --> 19:16.329
Can I ask you one thing?

19:16.331 --> 19:17.696
Of course. What?

19:17.698 --> 19:20.295
Did you look in my closet?

19:20.297 --> 19:22.631
No. Just the drawer.

19:22.633 --> 19:24.335
You promise you didn't
look in the closet?

19:24.337 --> 19:25.366
I promise.

19:25.368 --> 19:26.766
Why, what's in there?

19:26.768 --> 19:28.869
Don't worry about it.

19:28.871 --> 19:30.174
Good night.

